            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2043-v2-Step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> fine egg noodle nest[s]</strong> to a large bowl, cover with <strong>boiled water</strong> and stir for 10 secs to separate the noodles</p><p>Set aside to soak for 4 min</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
