    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add most of the <strong>spring onion </strong>(save the rest for garnish!), the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>pak choi white base</strong> and your <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> to the<strong> </strong>chicken and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
