      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>roasted peanuts</strong>, <strong>miso paste</strong>, <strong>honey</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and a splash of <strong>boiled water</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min further or until the sauce has thickened</p><p>Meanwhile, drain the <strong>noodles</strong> and stir through your <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame oil </strong>–<strong> </strong>these are your <strong>sesame noodles</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
